ious different enemies to destroy!</strong></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836280/extras/50ad01c78f8372e9622b2f159ffc816e.avif?t=1726965753\" width=622 height=192 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Interesting puzzles involving lots of explosions!</strong></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836280/extras/eafe792832eaee33a2c1249753de6f45.poster.avif?t=1726965753\" width=622 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836280/extras/eafe792832eaee33a2c1249753de6f45.webm?t=1726965753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836280/extras/eafe792832eaee33a2c1249753de6f45.mp4?t=1726965753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Traps everywhere!</strong></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836280/extras/65725bbd4fcb3ef39a2feb5007c49f46.poster.avif?t=1726965753\" width=622 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836280/extras/65725bbd4fcb3ef39a2feb5007c49f46.webm?t=1726965753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836280/extras/65725bbd4fcb3ef39a2feb5007c49f46.mp4?t=1726965753\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>And last but not least, Billy.</strong></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836280/extras/bee72238f0f377c7c9e3c27f3193baa3.apng?t=1726965753\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.ste